div.span: The Bastion-Host is the installationsserver of the SNO-Cluster-Nodes and has access to artifactory and the esx-sevrer and vcenter-server. it hosts the DNSMASQ (DNS-Server)

div.style: text-align: left;
text-align: left;
div.span: The Container-Build-Host is the server, which builds the Image with the Containerfile and pushes the Image to Artifactory. It must have access to the internet to download software and the content of the github-Repository. Optional. It can have access to the internal registry-server to push the builded image to the registry.
